metadata.name: sea-nic.starry.night
metadata.description:
Ahoy there, art and dental enthusiasts. "sea-nic.starry.night" is a one-of-a-kind NFT that playfully combines Van Gogh's iconic Starry Night with a splash of dental charm. This whimsical creation features a happy tooth aboard a ship, navigating through the hypnotic swirls of a star-filled sky.

In a tongue-in-cheek tribute to the legendary post-impressionist painter, this piece adds a twist to a timeless classic by introducing our toothy friend into the mix. It's the perfect blend of art and dentistry for those who enjoy a good pun and a unique take on dentistry.

The cherry on top: when you decide to snag one of our NFT, you'll not only own a funky piece of digital art but also get to spread some smiles by choosing a dental charity to receive the profits, leaving you grinning from ear to ear.

Hop aboard the "sea-nic.starry.night" and join us on this light-hearted, artful adventure while making a difference.
